These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, sunflower, iris, begonia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, martial-arts, comedy, mystery
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, dog, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, tram, van
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 2. the person who growssunflower is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 7. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Flower    | iris   | sunflower       | azalea | begonia   |
| Movie-Genre        | martial-arts    | mystery  | comedy      | spy |
| Pet         | frog      | chinchilla | dog         | cat   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | ship       | tram        | van   |

