.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk, mirinda, lemonade
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, malaysian, turkish
City: hamburg, hannover, edinburgh, new-york
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, tram, trike
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is the australian##1
3. the person driving the tram is the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person drinking milk is between the indian and the person driving the car##2
5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is the person driving the trike##1
7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
9. the indian is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Beverage           | almond-milk | milk | lemonade | mirinda |
| Nationality   | australian  | malaysian | indian         | turkish      |
| City         | edinburgh      | hannover    | new-york         | hamburg   |
| Transport     | car         | roller    | trike          | tram         |

