.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, peach, potato
House: ranch-style, futuristic, cape-cod, palace
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, turtle
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, mystery, musical, sports
 1. the cape-cod house is the person eating peach##1
 2. the ranch-style house is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the palace house##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 7. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 8. the owner of the cat is between the person watching musical movies and the futuristic house##2
 9. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
10. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Food          | grapefruit | potato  | cauliflower | peach      |
| House   | ranch-style       | palace    | futuristic      | cape-cod      |
| Pet           | turtle     | cat     | dog         | hedgehog   |
| Movie-Genre         | musical | action | mystery     | sports |

