There are 4 different nationalities: australian, canadian, french, polish
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse, rabbit, snake
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
2. the australian is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the french is the bluemaster-smoker##1
6. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the owner of the chinchilla and the polish##2
9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
| Hobby           | chess     | filmmaking | cooking | puzzles |
| Cigar   | tiparillo     | montecristo       | ritmeester      | bluemaster   |
| Nationality   | canadian   | australian   | polish    | french       |
| Pet           | chinchilla | horse        | rabbit    | snake        |

