.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, hedgehog, rabbit
House: gothic-revival, tower, ranch-style, townhouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, metal, reggae, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, cycling, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the tower house##3
 2. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
 3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 4. the townhouse house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the tower house##1
 9. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the fan of trance is between the owner of the cat and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Pet      | rabbit | cat | hedgehog     | guinea-pig       |
| House          | gothic-revival   | townhouse    | ranch-style | tower       |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | metal       | trance    | reggae     |
| Sport         | cycling  | ice-hockey  | badminton | basketball |

