 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
 8. the owner of the rabbit is the coach##1
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the lizard is the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | soy-milk   | coffee | almond-milk | fanta      |
| Color        | emerald | coral | green   | red     |
| Pet         | lizard     | cat    | mouse       | rabbit     |
