 3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
 5. the dunhill-smoker is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the chaman-smoker##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is the blend-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is between the bongani-smoker and the owner of the bird##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
10. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | collecting | hiking     | puzzles  | magic-tricks |
