There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, malaysian, pakistani, polish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, ice-hockey, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 3. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 4. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the polish is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the polish is the person who's hobby is camping##1
10. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the malaysian##1
11. the pakistani is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |     4     |
| Hobby      | camping      | board-games  | dancing | skydiving      |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | scooter   | airplane    | taxi    |
