 4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who likes black##1
 6. the person driving the trike is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person driving the jet-ski##2
 7. the person driving the trike is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the teacher##1
 9. the writer is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
11. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the writer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |       4       |
