.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, radish, watermelon
4 different games are played: domino, go, canasta, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
4 different pets are kept: turtle, rat, snake, frog
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 4. the person playing go is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the rat##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person playing go and the owner of the turtle##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the person playing chess##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person eating radish is the person playing go##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | blueberry | watermelon   | radish   | artichoke |
| Game           | domino   | canasta     | go   | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Pet         | turtle    | rat | frog | snake    |

 